title: Macedonian folk and urban folk music
description:
This is a compilation of older Macedonian (FYROM) music. It is two records. First one is made out of Urban folk music (starogradske). That music was mostly popular in the cities in the period at the beginning of the century and till second world war. Second cd is made of the most famous traditional folk songs. This are the song who were sung anywhere but mostly outside city's.
